modified_SQL_query: UPDATE staging.FTP_Unpivot SET EQ(staging.FTP_Unpivot.Funding_space_Component, cfg.ALM_LKP_Receiving_legal_entity.Funding_Component), EQ(staging.FTP_Unpivot.Receiving_Legal_Entity, cfg.ALM_LKP_Receiving_legal_entity.Receiving_Legal_Entity) FROM staging.FTP_Unpivot AS a INNER JOIN cfg.ALM_LKP_Receiving_legal_entity AS d ON EQ(staging.FTP_Unpivot.Funding_space_Component, cfg.ALM_LKP_Receiving_legal_entity.Funding_Component_Export)
